<p>"The Cinematography of Studio Ghibli", a book about Atsushi Okui, in charge of Ghibli's photography department since 1993, from cels to digital eras (he also worked on Akira, Gundam...).<br>
Featuring many documents, &amp; comments from Miyazaki, Tomino, Otomo.<br>
